        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, y999 is a safe and secure platform. The app uses encryption technology to protect your data and ensure fair gaming with RNG certification."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How can I withdraw my earnings?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "y999 offers fast and secure withdrawal methods. Simply go to your account, choose your preferred payment method, and request a withdrawal."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Can I play on the y999 Game APK from my mobile device?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, the y999 App is fully optimized for mobile devices, so you can play and earn on the go."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What games are available on the y999 App?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "y999 offers a variety of games, including cricket and football betting, casino games, slot machines, and card games."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Are there any bonuses or promotions?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, y999 Game offers exciting bonuses and promotions, including welcome bonuses and daily rewards for active players."
      }
    }
  ]
};
---

<Layout 
  title="y999 Game - Official Download | Play and Earn Real Cash" 
  description="Download the official y999 Game App for Android. Experience the best casino games, sports betting, and slot machines in Pakistan. Safe, secure, and fast withdrawals."
  keywords="y999 game, y999 apk, y999 download, y999 casino, y999 game app, y999 pakistan, y999 slots, online casino pakistan"
  includeWebsiteSchema={true}
>
  <Fragment slot="schema">
    <OrganizationSchema />
    <BreadcrumbSchema items={[
      { name: "Home", url: `${BASE}/` },
    ]} />
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />
  </Fragment>

  <Hero />
  <Description />
</Layout>
